Metadata: Stevensine, a novel alkaloid of an unidentified marine sponge

Marine sponges have yielded relatively few alkaloids. This study of an unidentified Micronesian sponge has resulted in the isolation of sceptrin and a new metabolite, stevensine, which possesses the 6,7-​dihydropyrrolo[​2,3-​c]azepin-​8-​one ring system.
